item.title: Steering Committees Organization Meeting
item.description: The original committees from Tama and Toledo, and others who wish to join the effort, are invited to meet and discuss organization, priorities, and next steps.

item.title: Wellmark Foundation Meeting
item.description: Denise has secured an online meeting, now set for Zoom rather than Microsoft Teams, for 1:00 pm on Tuesday, January 4, 2022, with Jon Werger from the Wellmark Foundation. Denise would like to have some interested participants join her in this online meeting. Please email Denise for a link to the meeting if needed. Additional details from Denise are here: I forwarded to you an invitation from Jon Werger with the Wellmark Foundation.
